<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 161 - 164. Dorsal habitus photographs of Cyphocoleus spp., environmental patina removed: 161, Cyphocoleus flavipes Yahoue; 162, Cyphocoleus bourailensis, Bourail; 163, Cyphocoleus subulatus, Mt. Koghi; 124, Cyphocoleus iledespinsensis, Ile des Pins." , "Figures 141 - 160. Male aedeagal median lobe and associated parameres of Cyphocoleus spp., dextral view: 141 - 152, Cyphocoleus globulicollis; 141, Aoupinie; 142, Me Maoya; 143, Col de Roussettes; 144, internal sac partially everted, Gelima; 145, Col d'Amieu; 146, Mt. Do; 147, internal sac everted, Ningua; 148 - 150, Mt. Dzumac Rd; 151 - 152, Mt. Koghi; 153, Cyphocoleus flavipes, Yahoue; 154, Cyphocoleus bourailensis, Bourail; 155 - 158, Cyphocoleus subulatus; 155, La Crouen; 156, Mt. Rembai; 157, Col d'Amieu; 158, Mt. Koghi; 159 - 160, Cyphocoleus iledespinsensis, Ile des Pins; 159, dextral view; 160, ventral view." , "Figures 137 - 140. Distribution maps of Cyphocoleus spp.: 137, Cyphocoleus cychroides, Cyphocoleus cordatus, Cyphocoleus cardiopterus; 138, Cyphocoleus latipennis; 139, Cyphocoleus globulicollis; 140 Cyphocoleus flavipes, Cyphocoleus bourailensis." , "Figures 113 - 120. Female right gonocoxae, ventral view, for Cyphocoleus spp. illustrating apical fringe setae of basal gonocoxite 1, and two lateral ensiform setae, one dorsal ensiform seta, and two apical nematiform setae on apical gonocoxite 2; 113, Cyphocoleus fasciatus, Mt. Panie; 114, Cyphocoleus cychroides, Pic d'Amoa; 115, Cyphocoleus latipennis Mt. Panie; 116, Cyphocoleus cordatus, Foret Nord; 117, Cyphocoleus globulicollis, Col des Roussettes; 118, Cyphocoleus flavipes, Noumea; 119, Cyphocoleus bourailensis, Bourail; 120, Cyphocoleus subulatus, Foret de Thi. Scale bar, 0.10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/111563" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/111562" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/111561" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/111556" .

